publisher			Caiysware							
publish_time	 2015年9月25日		
desc_long								关于这款游戏							Straima is an arena pulse-pumper platformer for 1-4 players, featuring a level editor.Master over 125+ devilishly difficult levels in your ravenous pursuit of pinky delicacy, spanning special powers, gameplay mutators and a co-op variant. There's also several 2-4 player game modes: Deathmatch, Handball and Gunslingers, allowing for chaotic chumily fun times. And finally a full feature level editor with 60+ object types allows you to design, save and share your inspired creations for immense joy.---Note the co-op and multiplayer game modes are local only, not online.						
